<div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-md w-full space-y-8">
    <div>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
        인증 링크가 만료되었습니다
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600">
        이메일 인증 링크는 24시간 동안만 유효합니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-md bg-red-50 p-4">
      <div class="flex">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-red-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-3">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800">
            인증 링크가 만료되었습니다
          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-red-700">
            <p>새로운 인증 링크를 받으려면 아래 버튼을 클릭하세요.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <%= form_with url: resend_confirmation_path, method: :post, local: true do |f| %>
        <% if @user %>
          <%= f.hidden_field :email, value: @user.email %>
        <% end %>

        <% unless @user %>
          <div>
            <%= f.label :email, "이메일 주소", class: "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700" %>
            <%= f.email_field :email, required: true, class: "mt-1 appearance-none rounded-md relative block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 placeholder-gray-500 text-gray-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 focus:z-10 sm:text-sm", placeholder: "이메일 주소" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <button type="submit" class="group relative w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
            재전송
          </button>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <%= link_to "홈으로 돌아가기", root_path, class: "text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
